{
  "stem": "16.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, listen, can you take a taxi day after tomorrow, come back, and see me without your uncle?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd like to talk to you without your uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I give him back his $10.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know how to get there by bus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lived on 90th street and Broadway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was on 57th and Broadway, Central Park.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I go back there on Thursday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, we talked for about an hour and a half.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it, it, it made me feel, somehow, a little better talking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to make the story short, I wound up going to this guy three times a week for nine months-- when I found out he's a psychiatrist that my uncle paid for, for me, $25 a visit because I was-- I was-- I, I was-- I didn't want to live.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have guilty feelings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did I remain alive, and not one of my brothers, or not my younger brother, one immediately younger?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a handsome guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Girls were hovering around him all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [CRYING] I just-- I was crying all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day-- one day, his relatives came to visit us, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle, he says, I want to ask you a question.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did it happen that my brother, your father, let himself be taken by the Germans, just like that?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- my answer was-- I just started to cry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even though I was taken from Romania, I mean, I just imagined myself-- what do you do when four Germans bust the door down with machine guns, roust everybody out?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, what do you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, I had an uncle, as it happens, he was shot on the street because he wasn't moving fast enough for them.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
